    content: `**The Three-Column Layout**\n\n**Left Column — Nation Stats Panel:**\nYour primary nation data: epoch, population, treasury, GDP, resources, tech level, and allies. This is your "at a glance" view of national health.\n\n**Center Column — World Map & Chat:**\nThe interactive hex world map occupies the center. Below or alongside it (depending on screen size) is the World Chat interface with Global/Allies/System channels and the Activity Ledger.\n\n**Right Column — Metrics & Market:**\nNation Metrics Panel (stability, manufacturing, defense, unit power) plus the live Stock Ticker feed scrolling all price movements.\n\n**Header Bar:**\nAll action buttons: Issue Stock, Tech Tree, Research, Manage, Workers, Exchange, Government, Global News, Build, Marketplace, Profile, Tutorial.\n\n**Mobile Layout:**\nOn mobile the three columns stack. The bottom scrollable bar contains the action buttons. Swipe horizontally to access all buttons.`,
