    content: `**The 12 Epochs**\n\nAdvancing requires: minimum Tech Points banked + all prerequisite techs unlocked.\n\n**Key Epoch Unlocks:**\n- Stone → Bronze: Bronze buildings, early military, first markets\n- Bronze → Iron: Iron Miners, iron construction, early diplomacy\n- Iron → Classical: Trade routes, universities, government buildings\n- Classical → Medieval: Walls, castles, guilds, mercantile economy\n- Medieval → Renaissance: Banking, printing press, advanced culture\n- Renaissance → Industrial: Factories, oil drilling, stock exchanges\n- Industrial → Modern: Global markets, corporate law, mass production\n- Modern → Digital: Internet, cyber infrastructure, digital currency\n- Digital → Information: AI research, data centers, information warfare\n- Information → Space: Orbital infrastructure, satellite defense\n- Space → Galactic: The final epoch — interstellar dominance\n\n**Cost Scaling:** Each epoch increases all construction costs ~15% and resource consumption ~10%.`,
    tips: ["Don't rush epochs — a well-built Stone Age economy beats a broke Renaissance nation.", "Epoch advances trigger a global announcement. Other players will know.", "The Industrial Age is the biggest transition — it unlocks stock exchanges and oil."]
