    content: `**Production Rate Formula**\n\nOutput = Workers × Base Rate × (1 + EpochIndex × 0.08)\n\n**Example at Industrial Age (epoch 6, mult 1.48):**\n- 3 Lumberjacks → 3 × 5 × 1.48 = 22 wood/tick\n- 2 Iron Miners → 2 × 3 × 1.48 = 8 iron/tick\n- 1 Oil Engineer → 1 × 6 × 1.48 = 8 oil/tick\n\n**Building Bonuses:**\n- Lumberyard: +20% to wood\n- Quarry: +20% to stone\n- Gold Mine: +20% to gold\n- Factory: Boosts Industrial Workers' manufacturing output\n\n**Priority by Era:**\n- Early (Stone-Bronze): Food + Wood + Stone\n- Mid (Iron-Classical): Gold + Iron\n- Late (Industrial+): Oil + Industrial Workers`,
