    content: `**Two Research Systems**\n\n**1. Tech Tree (instant unlocks):**\n- One-time Tech Point payment\n- Effect is immediate upon purchase\n\n**2. Research Panel (advanced projects):**\n- Continuous TP investment over multiple ticks\n- Researchers generate TP → invested into active project\n- Completion triggers global announcement if a Breakthrough\n\n**Tech Point Generation:**\nTP/tick = (Schools×1 + Universities×4) + (Pop×0.001) + (EducationSpending×0.1) + Other Building Bonuses\n\n**Storage Cap:**\nMax TP = 500 + Schools×1000 + Colleges×3000 + Universities×6000\n\nIf TP hits cap, excess is wasted. Build more education buildings.`,
